---
title: Spicy Tropical Jerk-Style Chicken Tacos with Mango Slaw & Lime Crema
description: Crank up the heat and take tacos for a tropical spin with sweet and fiery Jamaican-style jerk chicken that cooks up in a flash! Tuck that spicy chicken into warm flour tortillas, then top your tacos with a tangle of cabbage slaw studded with sweet mango, juicy tomato, and tangy lime juice, and dig right in.
